data.description: Enjoy this beautifully improved 2-story brick townhouse, located on a quiet cul de sac in the gated Memorial West Community. This classic home showcases 3 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, and boasts numerous custom improvements that remarkably enhance its appeal. Enter through grand double doors to a spacious living area with high ceilings and hardwood floors. The adjacent atrium provides natural lighting, perfect for daytime relaxation and stargazing. The custom-built kitchen features quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, subway tile backsplash, and cabinets with brushed nickel hardware. Upstairs lies the primary bedroom with a spacious walk-in closet, sliding mirrors, and a luxurious bath with a soaking tub and dual sink vanity. A balcony at the back offers a relaxing view of the Rivercrest treeline. Additional highlights include a 2-car garage, utility room, and community pool access. Enjoy proximity to parks and Memorial City Mall in this private community.
